Get ready ! It's time for battle !
<p>Use the <strong>entire keyboard</strong>, and be <strong>the fastest to tap</strong>, and give your opponent a sneaky slap !</p><p>And nothing can stop you from <strong>pushing your friend away</strong> from the keyboard.. Juste try not to destroy everything !<br/><br/><br/><strong>Enjoy :)</strong><br/><br/><br/><br/>(The game is still in development so don't mash and spam, it would not be fair play !)</p>
